130
00:09:25,982 --> 00:09:29,777
Men are nothing without the love of women.

131
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:42,248
KIM JIN-U: CAN YOU COME OUT FOR A SECOND?

132
00:09:42,331 --> 00:09:44,667
