-Do you know him?

151
00:11:49,750 --> 00:11:50,793
No.

152
00:11:51,710 --> 00:11:54,755
-Where was it again?
-I found this place...

153
00:11:55,047 --> 00:11:57,133
Look at this. Here.

154
00:12:10,271 --> 00:12:11,313
