260
00:21:31,623 --> 00:21:33,083
Your name was Baek...

261
00:21:34,543 --> 00:21:35,627
Jeong...

262
00:21:37,504 --> 00:21:38,380
Jeong-u.

263
00:21:38,964 --> 00:21:40,382
Right, Baek Jeong-u.

264
00:21:41,133 --> 00:21:42,509
"Jeong-u."

265
00:21:55,480 --> 00:21:56,732
LEE JI-HO

266
00:21:58,108 --> 00:21:59,985
BAEK JEONG-U

